optimized_sql: WITH date_filter AS MATERIALIZED (SELECT d_date_sk FROM date_dim WHERE d_year = 1998), item_filter AS MATERIALIZED (SELECT i_item_sk, i_item_id FROM item WHERE i_category = 'Sports'), cd_filter AS MATERIALIZED (SELECT cd_demo_sk FROM customer_demographics WHERE cd_gender = 'F' AND cd_education_status = 'College'), customer_ca_joined AS MATERIALIZED (SELECT c.c_customer_sk, c.c_birth_year, ca.ca_country, ca.ca_state, ca.ca_county FROM customer c INNER JOIN customer_address ca ON c.c_current_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk WHERE c.c_birth_month = 2 AND ca.ca_state IN ('AR', 'NY', 'TX')), fact_dimensions_join AS (SELECT ca.ca_country, ca.ca_state, ca.ca_county, i.i_item_id, cs.cs_quantity, cs.cs_list_price, cs.cs_coupon_amt, cs.cs_sales_price, cs.cs_net_profit, ca.c_birth_year FROM catalog_sales cs INNER JOIN date_filter d ON cs.cs_sold_date_sk = d.d_date_sk INNER JOIN item_filter i ON cs.cs_item_sk = i.i_item_sk INNER JOIN cd_filter cd ON cs.cs_bill_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk INNER JOIN customer_ca_joined ca ON cs.cs_bill_customer_sk = ca.c_customer_sk WHERE cs.cs_wholesale_cost BETWEEN 41 AND 46) SELECT i_item_id, ca_country, ca_state, ca_county, AVG(CAST(cs_quantity AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS agg1, AVG(CAST(cs_list_price AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS agg2, AVG(CAST(cs_coupon_amt AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS agg3, AVG(CAST(cs_sales_price AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS agg4, AVG(CAST(cs_net_profit AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS agg5, AVG(CAST(c_birth_year AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS agg6 FROM fact_dimensions_join GROUP BY ROLLUP (i_item_id, ca_country, ca_state, ca_county) ORDER BY ca_country, ca_state, ca_county, i_item_id LIMIT 100
